{"tid":225214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(真人真事) 廁所板的迷思","createTime":"2017-05-01T15:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T16:30:25.000Z","uid":51912,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b165ff9fd31ca87900cc1541890519ef6a927cb","tid":225214,"uid":51912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩同fd吹水傾開, <br />\n是咁的,<br />\n話說有一家人, 共4女1男<br />\n住同一屋簷下, 共用同一個廁所<br />\n男的間唔時去廁所會唔記得扲起塊板, 結果就會滴到塊板<br />\n咁, 好自然女s就會屌: &quot;扲返起塊廁板啦仆街&quot;<br />\n男既就會反駁話: &quot; 你地去完廁所自已扲返起, 咪唔會發生d咁既事囉&quot; <br />\n<br />\n完！<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得女人岩既(即一味鳩叫但又唔做野)<br />\n, 請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果覺得男人岩既(即你有你講, 我反正唔會受損既) , 請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申, 已俾負皮。<br />\n原因, 既然唔想件事發生, 又令唔到人聽你講, 咪自已揾方法解決。講到尾, 受害既又係自已"},{"pid":"3e1124de37d99ab8baba1ec011bc3781bb58c75f","tid":225214,"uid":51912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d139f990cfc6063bcc9173094f0b778e3e84c481","tid":225214,"uid":51912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1ffd5ce4f0f1f83224eb494145ce8d1a841e7e1","tid":225214,"uid":51912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:33:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f40b9a96310a170c29fe726a9368e9e3e92dd8f","tid":225214,"uid":51912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91844309b42032c317b509ed448ee6cbc58a7fc1","tid":225214,"uid":55375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"4個人住實有兩個廁所 分男女廁is ok"},{"pid":"8e230c2b3c24587a72ba7d2af7800a673118b6a0","tid":225214,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:33:57.000Z","msg":"虧佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f7aad69dc78c3b3044bc46c90cea